overview: At Smile Concepts in Pitt Street Sydney CBD we offer Implant Dentistry, Cosmetic Dentistry and all areas of General Dentistry.We look at you gums and see if they are bleeding or whether you have loose teeth, gum disease, gingivitis, bad breath. We also look at whether you are suffering from headaches due to bruxism, clenching or grinding. Diagnosis and treatments for snoring and sleep apnoea are available here too.The general services provided here are children dentistry, painfree dentistry, sedation dentistry, sleep dentistry, single visit root canal treatment, wisdom teeth, emergency dentistry, holistic dentistry.We are located on Level 4, 307 Pitt Street, Sydney NSW 2000. Our contact phone is (02) 9267 7777
